      <title>标普全球警告美国退出世界银行的风险“前所未有”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/sp-global-warns-unprecedented-us-world-bank-withdrawal-risk-2025-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球 (S&amp;P Global) 等顶级信用评级机构警告称，美国“前所未有”地退出世界银行和其他顶级多边贷款机构，将损害这些机构所珍视的 AAA 信用评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/sp-global-warns-unprecedented-us-world-bank-withdrawal-risk-2025-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 12:21:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
